results.name: Number of numbers less than or equal to n of the form 3^i*5^j.
formula: a(n) = Sum_{k=1..n} mu(15*k)*floor(n/k), where mu is the Möbius function (A008683).
maple: with(numtheory): seq(add(mobius(15*k)*floor(n/k), k=1..n), n=1..90); # _Ridouane Oudra_, Jul 29 2019
program: (MAGMA) [&+[MoebiusMu(15*k)*Floor(n/k):k in [1..n]]: n in [1..97]]; // _Marius A. Burtea_, Jul 30 2019
results.author: _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Sep 18 2005
